import { Image, Text, View } from "react-native"
import tw from "twrnc"

export default () => {
    return( 
    <View style = {tw`flex h-full w-full`}>
        <View  style = {tw`h-full w-2/3 justify-items-center border p-20`}>
            <View style = {tw`flex flex-col border border-1 border-orange-30`}>
                <Text style = {tw`font-bold text-3xl text-center`}>
                    WELCOME   BACK
                </Text>
            </View>    
        </View>
        <View>
            <Image />        
        </View>
    </View>
)}
